int set_log_level(int level)

This sets the log level for the object when using the function _log(). The log
level is an integer from 0 to 4, with 0 being silent or emergency messages
and the maximum being 4, which logs everything. The default log level is 1.

For the scale of messages you wish to log, please see help _log.

Related: query_log_level, _log, set_log_prefix, query_log_prefix
